		<section id="sect-Filtering_Hosts">
			<title>Filtering Hosts</title> 
			<para>
				The Host Filter accordion is provided to easily navigate through the hosts. Use the ones provided or create your own. In addition, you can set a default filter.
			</para>
			<xi:include href="topics/To_set_a_default_Host_Filter.xml" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" />
			<xi:include href="topics/To_create_a_Host_Filter.xml" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" />
		</section>
